data.text:
Born of personal heartbreak and crisis within her family, Blanca ("Who I Am") comes out with a song of surrender to a Power greater than that crisis.

Find out Blanca's very personal story behind this powerful song, "Greater is He".

Blanca has also launched a new social media campaign, the #RealTrueYou challenge! She has challenged fans, friends, and several other artists to participate, and the movement is also gaining support from a variety of partners, including Project Inspired, Jam The Hype, FaithGirlz, and Girls Of Grace. Join her by posting the #RealTrueYou on Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram!
